William Spencer (silent film actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Spencer_(silent_film_actor) 0 William J. Spencer was an American silent film actor. Spencer starred in 14 films between 1915 and 1921. He starred in films such as The Twinkler in 1916. William_J._Spencer was an_American_silent_film_actor .
